  "summary": "Emmett has a path traversal in internal assets handler",
  "details": "The RSGI static handler for Emmett's internal assets (`/__emmett__` paths) is vulnerable to path traversal attacks.\n\nAn attacker can use `../` sequences (eg `/__emmett__/../rsgi/handlers.py`) to read arbitrary files outside the assets directory.",
